ADDITIONAL SYSTEM INFORMATION :
OS: Ubuntu 22.04.2 LTS
OpenJDK compiled with debugslow from https://github.com/openjdk/jdk/ and commit 8d49ba9e8d3095f850b3007b56488a0c0cf8ddff

